library(tidyverse)
data %>%
  filter( %in% c('')) %>%
  mutate( = __ / _) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = , fill = )) + 
  geom_density(alpha = 0.3) + 
  labs(y = '') + 
  theme(legend.position = 'none', 
        axis.title.x=element_blank()) -> density_

data %>%
  filter( %in% c('')) %>%
  mutate( = __ / _) %>%
  group_by() %>%
  summarise(. = mean()) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = ., y = fct_relevel(, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''))) + 
  geom_col(fill = 'dark blue') + 
  geom_text(aes(label = round(., 2), x = .-2.5), color = 'white', size = 2.5) +
  labs(x = ' ', y = '') + 
  scale_y_discrete(limits=rev) -> bar_
